#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_basematerial3d.rst:751
msgid "enum **DistanceFadeMode**:"
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_basematerial3d.rst:753
msgid "**DISTANCE_FADE_DISABLED** = **0** --- Do not use distance fade."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_basematerial3d.rst:755
msgid ""
"**DISTANCE_FADE_PIXEL_ALPHA** = **1** --- Smoothly fades the object out "
"based on each pixel's distance from the camera using the alpha channel."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_basematerial3d.rst:757
msgid ""
"**DISTANCE_FADE_PIXEL_DITHER** = **2** --- Smoothly fades the object out "
"based on each pixel's distance from the camera using a dither approach. "
"Dithering discards pixels based on a set pattern to smoothly fade without"
" enabling transparency. On certain hardware this can be faster than "
":ref:`DISTANCE_FADE_PIXEL_ALPHA "
"<class_BaseMaterial3D_constant_DISTANCE_FADE_PIXEL_ALPHA>`."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_basematerial3d.rst:759
msgid ""
"**DISTANCE_FADE_OBJECT_DITHER** = **3** --- Smoothly fades the object out"
" based on the object's distance from the camera using a dither approach. "
"Dithering discards pixels based on a set pattern to smoothly fade without"
" enabling transparency. On certain hardware this can be faster than "
":ref:`DISTANCE_FADE_PIXEL_ALPHA "
"<class_BaseMaterial3D_constant_DISTANCE_FADE_PIXEL_ALPHA>`."
msgstr ""

